reviewText: The power of God is waiting for you. His love is eternal.
This is an amazing present-day movie about a miraculous healings of mind, body and soul of three teenage boys and their families and friends.  Love, love, love this movie.
Very, very good movie!  A good movie that the whole family can enjoy.  Some people gave it a very low rating because of " the box". Its not the box,  its their faith.
My purchase will be a wonderful addition to our video library.
A decent movie to watch if you are tired of watching so much  violence and lack of moral.

Wonderful movie.  Good story and true to billing.  In an age where hollywood is falling short, this was a fairly decent film.
I would recommend.

It is a very low budgeted film with horrible acting. The movie is not biblical at all. At the end of the movie a box with a nail that was supposedly one of the nails that was used to crucify Jesus heals a boy with cancer.
This movie is worth seeing.  I enjoyed!
